Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.74,0:04:07.03,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}哪一部是《彗星撞地球》 哪一部是《世界末日》？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Which one was Deep Impact and which one was Armageddon?
