Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.19,0:04:41.19,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}在客厅 那里有灯…\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}It's in the living room, where there's also a light...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.40,0:04:43.57,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}而且没有人会踢你小腿\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}...and no one will kick you in the shin.
