Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.80,0:06:26.59,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我是在想用逃生梯下去\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}I was thinking we'd just go down the fire escape.
